FBIS4-16585 "drsov074_b_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-074 Daily Report 16 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Establishes Presidential Group of Experts Yeltsin Establishes Presidential Group of Experts LD1604141094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1300 GMT 16 Apr 94 LD1604141094 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] Boris Yeltsin has decided to set up a group of experts under the Russian president. An edict signed by him says the group will consist of eight people. Their names have not been given. Among other things, the experts will draft proposals regarding the implementation of the president's decisions in the economic sphere. They will also compile speeches for him, as well as analytical and information memos.
